{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, UID_1B= 0 marks the Hard sources that have no counterpart within their matching radius in the 1B catalogues.",
    "Following this procedure, we find 780 \"Hard-only\" sources; of these, 764 are point-like (EXT = 0) and 16 extended (EXT > 0).",
    "Figure 8 displays the count rate distribution of the hard-band selected sources in the 0.6-2.3 Fig. 8.",
    "Distributions of 0.6-2.3 keV (x-axis) and 2.3-5 keV (y-axis) count rates of the hard-band selected sources.",
    "The \"Hard-only\" sources are marked in red colour."
  ]
}